title: Final: USC, Steve Sarkisian lose to Washington, 17-12
text: Final: USC, Steve Sarkisian lose to Washington, 17-12 Oct. 8, 2015 Updated 10:15 p.m. 1 of 22 USC wide receiver Steven Mitchell Jr., right, tries to get close to the end zone after making a catch late during the second quarter of Thursday's game against Washington at the Coliseum. Mitchell left the game with a sprained ankle.
